 the rent, and takes college courses, rarely making it to class. Determined to forge her own path, she refuses to take the reins of her father\'s global empire just as staunchly as she rejects the idea that he\'s truly gone. Advised to face the facts and move forward after seven years without him, even Lara can\'t understand what drives her to finally solve the puzzle of his mysterious death. Going explicitly against his final wishes, she leaves everything she knows behind in search of her dad\'s last-known destination: a fabled tomb on a mythical island that might be somewhere off the coast of Japan. But her mission will not be an easy one; just reaching the island will be extremely treacherous. Suddenly, the stakes couldn\'t be higher for Lara, who-against the odds and armed with only her sharp mind, blind faith and inherently stubborn spirit-must learn to push herself beyond her limits as she journeys into the unknown. If she survives this perilous adventure, it could be the making of her, earning her the name tomb raider.','/images/nowShowing/ePyN2nX9t8SOl70eRW47Q29zUFO.jpg','[{\"cast_id\":1,\"character\":\"Lara Croft\",\"credit_id\":\"57228f82c3a368759c0002f4\",\"gender\":1,\"id\":227454,\"name\":\"Alicia Vikander\",\"order\":0,\"profile_path\":\"/drJX0oFv1wQAqFo3lr2ZpLdr2xx.jpg\"},{\"cast_id\":4,\"character\":\"Mathias Vogel\",\"credit_id\":\"5848703b92514119ad00b230\",\"gender\":2,\"id\":27740,\"name\":\"Walton Goggins\",\"order\":1,\"profile_path\":\"/gA5nf2alzIPPjs1MSjS1PmrCedJ.jpg\"},{\"cast_id\":7,\"character\":\"Richard James Croft\",\"credit_id\":\"588b793fc3a3683c3d000058\",\"gender\":2,\"id\":17287,\"name\":\"Dominic West\",\"order\":2,\"profile_path\":\"/56zmVMiuUhqas13xn700hvXUA32.jpg\"},{\"cast_id\":5,\"character\":\"Lu Ren\",\"credit_id\":\"5876975ec3a3682d33001325\",\"gender\":2,\"id\":64436,\"name\":\"Daniel Wu\",\"order\":3,\"profile_path\":\"/mIa3Dj2ailEg2vYpBLJdfByhAHe.jpg\"},{\"cast_id\":11,\"character\":\"Ana Miller\",\"credit_id\":\"5a1949